## Project Context

This project uses `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` as the central reference for resource nicknames and IDs.

When the user refers to resources by nickname (e.g., "Main Flow", "Results Board", "Playground"), look up the actual IDs in `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`.

- Always read `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` before calling n8n, Monday, or Slack MCP tools to resolve nicknames to real IDs.
- Use the Playground/sandbox Slack channel for testing unless the user says otherwise.
